The paper also discusses the existence of distance k-sectors, which is related to geometric routing and graph theory (cs.GR). The use of proper geodesic spaces suggests a connection to metric geometry (cs.MG), and the mention of the Knaster-Tarski fixed point theorem suggests a connection to numerical analysis (cs.NA).
